HEADWORD: Imaginable
<hw>Im*ag"i*na*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>imaginabilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>imaginable</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Capable of being imagined; conceivable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Men sunk into the greatest darkness <qex>imaginable</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Tillotson.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Im*ag"i*na*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
